title: VSee Clinic for Patient
description:
VSee Clinic is a simple, secure way for you to hold a telehealth consultation with your provider from anywhere. VSee Clinic allows HIPAA-compliant chat and video calls. It’s encrypted, so your patient health data is secure.

Seeing your doctor is easy with VSee Clinic. You can schedule a consultation or “walk in” without an appointment. You can also make credit card payments, review your visit history, and read your doctor’s notes – all from your Android device.
